        <num>CC 300</num>
        <heading>300.  Provisional administration pending consideration of excuse</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 300.  Provisional administration pending consideration of excuse.
During the time of the pendency of the litigation relative to the validity of his excuses, the tutor who is appointed shall be bound provisionally* to administer as such, until he shall have been regularly discharged.
* &quot;Provisionally&quot; has no counterpart in French text.</p>
        </content>
